Coronavirus closures: Disney World, Disneyland halt annual passholder paymentsCLOSE The coronavirus wasn't stopping this Texas family from feeling the Disney magic from their own home.
StoryfulThe expiration date for promotional child tickets will be extended to Dec. 15, 2020, or 13 days after the ticket's first use, whichever comes first.
Walt Disney World resort tickets in Florida are also not refundable, but can be used on any date through Dec. 15, 2020.
Tickets that have not been used by that date can be used toward the purchase of a future ticket.
Disneyland Resort and Walt Disney World Resort hotel reservations can be made for June 1 or later.